
    V I D E O   4   L I N U X   C O N T R O L
    =========================================


This program is based on xawtv code.
It allow get or set value of ALL controls supported by v4l devices.

For correct output of dump (-d parameter) must v4l driver support flag V4L2_CTRL_FLAG_NEXT_CTRL.


USAGE: 
  v4lctrl [options]
  options:
    -h            print this text
    -c file       use <file> as video4linux device
    -d            dump device informations
    -g cid        get value of control with id <cid>
    -s cid        set control with id <cid> to value specified in parameter -v
    -v value      value for set


COMPILE:
  
    autoheader
    automake
    autoconf

    ./configure
    
    make
    
    
RUN:
  
  ./src/v4lctrl

